{"tid":483014,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢文]一口氣睇晒四季+劇場版魔法少女伊莉雅","createTime":"2017-11-28T17:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T10:16:42.000Z","uid":8203,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b597e01319b6778dcaa0ed355a54b3f211465d29","tid":483014,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:04:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老母佛都有火用撚左半個鐘打文<br />\n剪下然後成篇文唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的，前排有人係到開post問fate系列邊套最好睇<br />\n點知樓主比人屌到反肚話咁長既list偏偏欠缺左魔伊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我先開始睇由silver link製作既四季fate外傳<br />\n點知咁就中晒毒了<br />\n雷切定千鳥 fz定fsn好睇？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">魔伊世界第一</span></span>呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n說來慚愧我係由ubw tv版開始播然後D人話睇左fz先再睇fsn<br />\n我先開始接觸fate呢套巨作<br />\n但原來我錯過得更大既係魔伊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無錯我係死毒撚 我最中意廢萌<br />\n但魔伊唔只有萌 而且有一流既打鬥<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3YhfEPxVxNY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3YhfEPxVxNY&d=Mu1uKurn9zdcSqIMyEx0GP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=35690ceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3YhfEPxVxNY</a><br />\n剩係伊莉雅呢下掃堂腿已經J到我精囊出血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然呢part好似已經係最好睇既打鬥<br />\n<br />\n講埋歌<br />\nOP starlog我好耐之前已經聽過下<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ovxsq-cqSlo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOvxsq-cqSlo&d=Mu1uKurn9zdcSqIMyEx0GP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=79207cfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ovxsq-cqSlo</a><br />\n星は変わる世界の闇と夜を照らして<br />\n一聽到呢句精華先知原來呢首出自魔伊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且三期OP亦令我正式成為fhana飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hVl4oxOST70\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhVl4oxOST70&d=Mu1uKurn9zdcSqIMyEx0GP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=73f05647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hVl4oxOST70</a><br />\n下年一定去睇live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOP既動畫亦做得越來越出色<br />\n好似三期伊莉雅用合體變身拉美游隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同四期頭四五秒果個分鏡<br />\n<br />\n人設內容我呢d業餘都不如既小薯仔就唔講了<br />\n總之就好撚好睇<br />\n無奈係三期頭半季完全係講校園仲要BL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但第四季第一集就要伊莉雅孤令令去冰天雪地既異世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沉重到我一時就間都追唔到落去<br />\n伊莉雅好撚可愛 配音仲要昇華埋<br />\n屌佢老母ufo成日醜化伊莉雅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而美游就唔洗講啦 簡直就係完美既女神<br />\npure到true到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n魔伊仲破左幾多傳統好引人入勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n魔法少女竟然係換上英靈服裝<br />\n女一會變身女二既裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且無主角威能 三期輸到仆街<br />\n<br />\n岩岩睇埋劇場版真係好撚精彩<br />\n雖然作畫係差小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n節奏又有d亂<br />\n不過有幾可會睇士郎咁撚型<br />\n成撚日話要做正義の味方<br />\n屌你老味終於搵到囉<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可愛就係惟一既正義 守護可愛既妹妹就係正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n而劇場版仲要完全補充番美游既身世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而士郎仲要出埋日文版既ubw大絕<br />\n又成功啟動到聖杯<br />\n相信好多睇開fate既觀眾都有好大既欣慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家睇到我唔買開fig都想破戒買fig<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最緊要好想買到呢本呀屌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gamers-onlineshop.jp/sphone/products/detail.php?product_id=10331349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamers-onlineshop.jp%2Fsphone%2Fproducts%2Fdetail.php%3Fproduct_id%3D10331349&d=Mu1uKurn9zdcSqIMyEx0GP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=f9ab9ad8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gamers-onlineshop.jp/sphone/products/detail.php?product_id=10331349</a><br />\n<br />\n睇晒咁多集 而家好空虛 空虛到打咁長既廢文<br />\n幾時出下一季呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498647c3581d468961eec7cdfec0ffcb531c4ce8","tid":483014,"uid":8203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲未睇既你好快快趣去睇 唔睇後悔終生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n發現原來自己仲未睇ova<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89dad06044a5d6e297e4d130ae915090643e83a","tid":483014,"uid":84128,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:09:49.000Z","msg":"睇漫畫版好過睇動畫"},{"pid":"b47b57ca735d71638f25fdb081eceea96703f30e","tid":483014,"uid":143411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:10:20.000Z","msg":"師兄真識貨 伊莉雅賽高"},{"pid":"953002a2d85473424a756892fa54e26fe68c2f1c","tid":483014,"uid":8307,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:13:45.000Z","msg":"最衰就係間公司冇錢,後個幾季同劇場版都畫崩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48db12e8aa0211d736d207a663bf90d44cbe246f","tid":483014,"uid":17352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇漫畫版好過睇動畫</blockquote><br />\n漫畫仲高質 必睇"},{"pid":